  <brief_title>Riociguat in Children With Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension (PAH)</brief_title>
  <acronym>PATENT-CHILD</acronym>
  <official_title>Open-label, Individual Dose Titration Study to Evaluate Safety, Tolerability and Pharmacokinetics of Riociguat in Children From 6 to Less Than 18 Years of Age With Pulmonary Arterial Hypertension (PAH)</official_title>
